<h2>Welcome</h2>

<p>I am Junpei Zhong (Joni), a research associate (fulltime PhD) at <a href="http://www.uni-hamburg.de/index_e.html" target="_blank">University
of Hamburg</a>, under the supervision of <a
href="http://www.informatik.uni-hamburg.de/~wermter/" target="_blank">Prof. Dr.
Stefan Wermter</a>. My work is also involved in and sponsored by the <a
href="http://www.robotdoc.org/" target="_blank">RobotDoc Collegium</a>, a
multi-national doctoral training network on developmental robotics.</p>
